  "G. Gnanalingam chairs Westports Holdings, a multi-cargo port operator that he cofounded with Ahmayuddin bin Ahmad.",
  "The group owns a 60-year concession to operate and expand its container terminals in Pulau, Indah and Port Klang, which will end in 2054.",
  "Westports is one of three main port operators in the Straits of Malacca that handle gateway and transhipment container cargo.",
  "His son, Ruben Emir Gnanalingam, is Westports' managing director. "
